                        <interp inst="t18350202-name-171" type="surname" value="MEREDITH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18350202-name-171" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS MEREDITH</persName>
                  </hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">re-examined</hi>. The journeyman's wages of these boots</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183502020028"></xptr>
               <p>cost me 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I only repair them to fill the men's time up, and pay them the same wages as I do for a bespoke pair—the leather would be worth 14<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., besides the labour and patches, which are 2<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—any man must know they are worth more than 9<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.</p>
